data.Name: Dirty Bird
data.Bio: There are multiple artists with this name 1) Dirty Bird is a music producer, visual artist, and tech hobbyist from North Carolina. He specializes in electronic music, Y2K aesthetics, and afro-futurism. 2) Dirty Bird is a Hardcore/Punk band from Toronto, Ontario, endorsing themselves as "Canada's drunkest hardcore band". Formed in 1993, they've been billed with other notable groups such as The Misfits, Nashville Pussy, Dayglo Abortions, DOA, Gang Green, New Bomb Turks, UK Subs, Death Sentence, and The Vibrators.
